</div><div class="sect1 adoc">
<h2 id="checkout">3. Installing the Ceres checkout in Callisto</h2>
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>You want to use the new checkout with its plugin capability and individualisation in concert with your Callisto online store? No problem – read here how to do it step by step. And if you need more assistance, visit our service section in the <a href="https://marketplace.plentymarkets.com/services/CeresCheckout4Callisto_5475" target="_blank" rel="noopener">marketplace</a>.</p>
</div>
